ww.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;  拼夕夕又出充电头了[受虐滑稽]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/d73e0eb4e0c23f54c3fb5c345cbc457a.jpeg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/cabfa32dcc66fefb24e772cbdb59afb5.jpeg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/71695590</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/71695590</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 05:23:54 GMT</pubDate><author>兔子不吃萝卜丫</author></item><item><title>充电的话还需要再接电池保护板吗？手机电池正负极直接接蓝牙板子上，目前没充电</title><description>&lt;p&gt;充电的话还需要再接电池保护板吗？手机电池正负极直接接蓝牙板子上，目前没充电&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/461252a36d265037bbb7010b587fe3a4.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/bac7e8ab5dd848258b70dd7cce12d654.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/96d24589e46883dda6e16aa631813e34.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/d1a8a64762201880bbc93cb2a7eee729.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/f47f0d79dad1b239b703da316649805b.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/18263925c11bdcfdbe10cf151c345279.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/71681601</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/71681601</guid><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 10:48:03 GMT</pubDate><author>诚与生俱来</author></item><item><title>#DIY# 有个问题想请教一下各位大佬，就是我有个淘汰下来的小米10u双电芯电池，可以把它拆成两块，在改成给小风扇供电的电池可以吗[坏笑][坏笑][坏笑]#数码日常# ...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;  有个问题想请教一下各位大佬，就是我有个淘汰下来的小米10u双电芯电池，可以把它拆成两块，在改成给小风扇供电的电池可以吗[坏笑][坏笑][坏笑]&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E6%95%B0%E7%A0%81%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8?type=0&quot;&gt;#数码日常#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E5%B0%8F%E9%A3%8E%E6%89%87?type=0&quot;&gt